Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.19,0:13:17.28,Dialog Yuragi-sou,,0,0,0,,Just wait a little longer.␀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.60,0:13:21.46,Dialog Yuragi-sou,,0,0,0,,Can't help it then.␀
