Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.62,0:17:56.29,Dialog Yuragi-sou,,0,0,0,,You're right!␀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.29,0:17:59.92,Dialog Yuragi-sou,,0,0,0,,Then the only missing was Nakai-san, and Koyuzu-chan.␀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.52,0:18:03.03,Dialog Yuragi-sou,,0,0,0,,Kogarashi-chan too!␀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.00,0:18:05.70,Dialog Yuragi-sou,,0,0,0,,Isn't he a male?␀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.70,0:18:09.16,Dialog Yuragi-sou,,0,0,0,,About that, how about wearing a swimsuit?␀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.62,0:18:12.28,Dialog Yuragi-sou Italic,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I'm already here.␀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.28,0:18:14.79,Dialog Yuragi-sou Italic,,0,0,0,,And last time was already bad.␀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.09,0:18:18.45,Dialog Yuragi-sou Italic,,0,0,0,,I already tried to return to normal.␀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.84,0:18:21.80,Dialog Yuragi-sou Italic,,0,0,0,,And here i've thought i've gotten stronger after training.␀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.80,0:18:25.84,Dialog Yuragi-sou Italic,,0,0,0,,But now that i can't even throw a punch,\Ni've become totally useless.␀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.82,0:18:29.36,Dialog Yuragi-sou Italic,,0,0,0,,This feeling of hopeless, is?␀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.51,0:18:33.12,Dialog Yuragi-sou Italic,,0,0,0,,Could this be the result of the soap.␀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.51,0:18:35.12,Dialog Yuragi-sou Italic,,0,0,0,, being rinsed away?␀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.92,0:18:39.42,Dialog Yuragi-sou Italic,,0,0,0,,If they end up using all the soap then what will happen to me?␀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.47,0:18:41.43,Dialog Yuragi-sou Italic,,0,0,0,,Damn it.␀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.10,0:18:43.12,Dialog Yuragi-sou Italic,,0,0,0,,Nobody..␀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.67,0:18:46.06,Dialog Yuragi-sou Italic,,0,0,0,,Even Yuuna doesn't even notice me.␀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.12,0:18:53.44,Dialog Yuragi-sou Italic,,0,0,0,,Am i going to stay like this and get washed away?␀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.34,0:18:58.51,Dialog Yuragi-sou,,0,0,0,,Everyone is the Hotspring's temperature okay?␀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.51,0:18:59.74,Dialog Yuragi-sou Italic,,0,0,0,,Nakai-san!␀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.74,0:19:01.39,Dialog Yuragi-sou,,0,0,0,,Where's Koyuzu-san?␀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.39,0:19:04.04,Dialog Yuragi-sou,,0,0,0,,She already went back to sleep.␀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.04,0:19:05.46,Dialog Yuragi-sou Italic,,0,0,0,,Went back to sleep?␀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.46,0:19:10.22,Dialog Yuragi-sou,,0,0,0,,Today the bath is sparkling clean as well. Thank you for cleaning it always!␀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.22,0:19:13.16,Dialog Yuragi-sou,,0,0,0,,Ah, no. Today, it's Kogarashi's turn to clean it.␀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.16,0:19:15.70,Dialog Yuragi-sou,,0,0,0,,He's a good help sometimes.␀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.70,0:19:17.97,Dialog Yuragi-sou,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so?␀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.31,0:19:21.12,Dialog Yuragi-sou,,0,0,0,,Kogarashi-kun is a good guy, right?␀
