Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.23,0:19:29.41,Dialog Yuragi-sou,,0,0,0,,He always does his job whole-heartedly.␀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.06,0:19:35.70,Dialog Yuragi-sou,,0,0,0,,It's Kogarashi-kun after all. Get along with him, Okay?␀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.70,0:19:38.97,Dialog Yuragi-sou,,0,0,0,,I'm not really close to him.␀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.55,0:19:42.78,Dialog Yuragi-sou,,0,0,0,,But well, he really doesnt seem like a bad person.␀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:47.07,Dialog Yuragi-sou,,0,0,0,,Yes! I'm always getting along well with Kogarashi-san!␀
