Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:51.80,Dialog Yuragi-sou,,0,0,0,,He's also cute, right?␀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.80,0:19:57.29,Dialog Yuragi-sou,,0,0,0,,Being a the first man here.\Nand also posessing spiritual powers,␀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.29,0:20:00.09,Dialog Yuragi-sou,,0,0,0,,At first i was worried how it will go.␀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.09,0:20:03.33,Dialog Yuragi-sou,,0,0,0,,But i'm glad it was a person like Kogarashi-kun who came.␀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.61,0:20:04.77,Dialog Yuragi-sou Italic,,0,0,0,,I also,␀
